short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome extension to generate code from HTTP requests

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rektocode is a devtools extension that helps you monitor HTTP requests and convert them into other programming languages such as JavaScript, Golang, Curl, etc.

Supported Programming languages:
- Javascript Fetch
- Curl
- Golang
- More to come, soon!

Rektocode is open source and any contribution are much appricated.

Bug report: https://github.com/majidsajadi/rektocode/issues/new?assignees=&labels=&template=bug_report.md&title=
